  {
    "task": "unfair_tos",
    "hf_index": 10,
    "text": "certain areas of the site ( and your access to or use of certain services or collective content ) may have different terms and conditions posted or may require you to agree with and accept additional terms and conditions . \n",
    "label_set": [
      "limitation_of_liability",
