  },
  {
    "task": "unfair_tos",
    "hf_index": 14,
    "text": "if you accept or agree to these terms on behalf of a company , university or other legal entity , you represent and warrant that you have the authority to bind that company , university or other legal entity to these terms and , in such event , `` you '' and `` your '' will refer and apply to that company or other legal entity . \n",
