  },
  {
    "task": "unfair_tos",
    "hf_index": 23,
    "text": "in order to access certain features of the site and services and to post any member content on the site or through the services you must register to create an account ( `` account '' ) and become a member . \n",
    "label_set": [
      "limitation_of_liability",
