    "task": "unfair_tos",
    "hf_index": 45,
    "text": "if you elect to purchase an annual subscription , we ( or our third party payment processor ) will automatically charge you on the anniversary of the commencement of your subscription using the payment information you have provided . \n",
    "label_set": [
