  {
    "task": "unfair_tos",
    "hf_index": 46,
    "text": "if you elect to purchase a monthly subscription , we ( or our third party payment processor ) will automatically charge you each month , on the calendar day corresponding to the commencement of your subscription , using the payment information you have provided . \n",
    "label_set": [
